{{rommap|game=Dragon Quest I & II (SNES)}}

This is the ROM map for ''Dragon Quest I & II'' (SNES). This compilation contains enhanced remakes of the first two Dragon Quest games on a single cartridge.

==ROM Header==
The ROM uses the standard SNES header format.

{| class="wikitable"
! Offset !! Size !! Description
|-
| $00ffc0 || 21 || Internal ROM name ("DRAGON QUEST I.II")
|-
| $00ffd5 || 1 || ROM makeup byte ($31 = HiROM, FastROM)
|-
| $00ffd6 || 1 || ROM type ($02 = ROM + SRAM)
|-
| $00ffd7 || 1 || ROM size ($0a = 1MB)
|-
| $00ffd8 || 1 || SRAM size ($03 = 8KB)
|-
| $00ffd9 || 1 || Region code ($00 = Japan)
|-
| $00ffda || 1 || Developer ID ($b2 = Enix)
|-
| $00ffdb || 1 || Version ($00)
|-
| $00ffdc || 2 || Checksum complement
|-
| $00ffde || 2 || Checksum
|-
| $00ffe0 || 32 || Native mode vectors
|}

